## ğŸ”¹ **API Endpoints**  

ğŸ“Œ **Authentication**  
- `POST /api/auth/register` â†’ Register new users  

ğŸ“Œ **Transactions**  
- `POST /api/transactions/send-money` â†’ Send money to another user  
- `POST /api/transactions/cash-in` â†’ Deposit money to user balance  
- `POST /api/transactions/cash-out` â†’ Withdraw money  

ğŸ“Œ **User Management**  
- `GET /api/users?email=user@example.com` â†’ Get user details  
- `GET /api/users/approved` â†’ List approved users  

ğŸ“Œ **Admin Management**  
- `GET /api/admin/pending-agents` â†’ Get pending agent requests  
- `PUT /api/admin/approve-agent` â†’ Approve agent registration  

